{"id":133720,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/01/赌王何鸿燊「千亿分家」奇案事件簿/","date":"2011-01-27T02:22:16Z","modified":"2011-01-27T02:22:16Z","title":"赌王何鸿燊「千亿分家」奇案事件簿","content":"<p><p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">赌王何鸿燊「千亿分家」奇案事件簿</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">赌王何鸿燊还活着，家属开始上演争产奇案，何到底要如何分割千亿家产，波谲云诡，成为一出活生生的豪门大戏。</span></span></p>\n<p><p><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">证券公司发表报告称，何鸿燊将自己所持有的</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.8</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">％澳娱股份转移至入</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lanceford</span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">……</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（此处省略股份转让的细节，反正与你我无关；若您有兴趣，只须知道，经如此这般转让后，何鸿燊只保留</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">股澳娱普通股，因此不再于</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">STDM–</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">投资公司持有之澳博股份中拥有应占权益。）</span></span></p>\n<p><p><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日上午</span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">媒体报道：自称何鸿燊代表律师的高国骏（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Gordon Oldham</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）向媒体指出，其当事人何鸿燊惊恐地发现，其于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Lanceford</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">持股量由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">％至上月只剩下少于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">％，控股权则被转移至三太陈婉珍 ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<h4>要翻墙? <a href=\"http://83920.info\">用赛风</a>.</h4>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8800]}